{"tid":392518,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"阿信屋賣工廈單位救亡？套現5200萬減低負債！","createTime":"2017-09-08T14:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T17:03:32.000Z","uid":17738,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c177e7b94edaef157f1af76f730af0ef3dbff52","tid":392518,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:14:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170908/large/1504876153_18bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170908%2Flarge%2F1504876153_18bb.jpg&h=23730496&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n759阿信屋母企CEC國際（759）宣布將出售觀塘一工廈單位，套現5,200萬元，交易於今年12月6日前落實，集團解釋，過去購入物業作營運用途，但考慮到已終止該物業營運並於今年4月出租，故此售出並降低集團負債及用作一般營運資金。該物業於2015年4月時以4,280萬元買入。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，截至今年4月底止，CEC國際銀行借貸額為6.09億元，按年跌10.3%，資本負債比率為52%。該公司稱，年內成功爭取與主要銀行重續銀行融資，今年4月向一間銀行爭取到3年期有抵押貸款6,000萬元，而未動用的銀行融資額逾3億元，亦不察覺主要銀行有意撤回融資或要求提前償還借款。<br />\n<br />\nCEC國際去年全年虧損擴大至5,000萬元，其中阿信屋業務全年蝕近3,000萬元，老闆林偉駿在公告上認低威，指「集團創下38年來最差業績，負責營運之創辦人深感歉疚」，為救亡，林偉駿更有意重啟電子元件製造業務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57186493&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57186493%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170908&d=7it%2F1bFr0qyUD3o5YqEL86MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=e4cd3d43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57186493%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170908&h=cf7b7e09\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57186493&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170908</a>"},{"pid":"45869c182cdb80e0bc405782b503f65413b2e369","tid":392518,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:17:15.000Z","msg":"而家先走返去開廠仲有得做？"},{"pid":"0761f3459c5ecad7744672e